---
title: Pork Ramen Bar One recipe—endless ways to enjoy!
description: Rich broth, tender meat and veggies, and a tangle of chewy noodles—we love ramen! For a family-style spin, you’ll set out noodles, gingery broth, bok choy, cabbage, carrots, savory ground pork, and savory-sweet hoisin sauce, and everyone can build their own bowl! Order rice on the side for a rice bowl, or add crispy fried onions for a tasty topper!
